    <div class="fancytext">WELCOME</div>
    <p>The Madawaska Valley Public Library was established in 1960 and throughout the years has seen much growth, not only in content, but in physical facilities as well. </p>
    <p>The  Madawaska Valley Public  Library has become an integral part of the community's life. It is committed to the growth and overall benefit of its patrons and our community as a whole.</p>
