   <div id="homeContent">
        
          <div class="hometext"><p>We have juggled our hours of operation so that we can offer better morning and after work hours. As of November 1, 2013 the library will be open from 1:00 - 5:00 on Mondays, Wednesdays & Fridays and from 1:00 - 7:00 p.m. on Tuesdays, 10:00 - 5:00 p.m. on Thursdays, and 9:00 - 1:00 p.m. on Saturdays. These changes were initiated with feedback from you, our library users and from surveying library usage. We hope these changes will increase your opportunities to visit the library.
</p></div>
